              Redefined
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-2xl">
            Experience the pinnacle of sophistication with PeakWares' meticulously curated collection of premium lifestyle essentials.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Premium CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 pt-4">
          <a href="/collections/exclusive" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hover:shadow-amber-500/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
            <span class="text-lg">Discover Exclusives</span>
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 ml-3 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
